results.title: DCE future not a distraction for Manly: Trbojevic
results.description: Daly Cherry-Evans won't be making an announcement on his future plans "any time soon", but Tom Trbojevic is insistent it's not an issue for him or Manly.

results.title: Shooting suspect appears in court as victims and their dog lie in state
results.description: Former President Joe Biden paid tribute to Minnesota's former speaker of the House and her spouse on Friday as they lie in state beneath the rotunda of the Minnesota State Capitol.

results.title: Desperate search for missing hiker
results.description: A huge search operation is underway for a missing hiker who was dropped off for a camping trip three days ago and failed to return.
